The following code:
```scala
class Foo {  
  def foo(x: AnyRef): Unit = {
    x.isInstanceOf[Tuple2[_, Tuple1[_]]]
    ()
  }
}
```

crashes on latest 2.10.x branch (including 2.10.0-M7):

